This project is for Coursera course Developing Data Products week 4 assignment. First, you will create a Shiny application and deploy it on Rstudio's servers. Second, you will use Slidify or Rstudio Presenter to prepare a reproducible pitch presentation about your application. 

Following files are included:

- This README.md gives brief introduciton.
- BMI Tool web based application is generated by Shiny of RStudio. The source files are ui.R and server.R.
- BMIToolIntro.html is presentation for this BMI Tool introduciton. It is also published under RPubs https://rpubs.com/KeepLearning/651985.
- BMIToolIntro.Rmd contains the R source code for generating the presentation report.
